releaseNotes:
This release contains the following:&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;* SL6&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;APEL 1.5.1 - Add support for Torque 5.1.2 time duration format; change dirq call to use absolute path to support versions of dirq &amp;gt;= 1.7; fix crash when StAR loader encouters a valid XML file with no records in it.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;APEL-SSM 2.1.7 - Added a delay when receiver is reconnecting to improve reliability. Improved the log output for SSM receivers so that there are fewer trivial entries and so it's more useful in tracking messages on the filesystem. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;CVMFS 2.3.5 - various bug fixes (see&lt;a href=&quot;http://cvmfs.readthedocs.io/en/2.3/cpt-releasenotes.html&quot;&gt; release notes&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;DynaFed 1.3.1 - various bug fixes and improvements (see &lt;a href=&quot;http://lcgdm.web.cern.ch/dynafed-131-available-epel-testing&quot;&gt;release notes&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;ARC 15.03.14 - bugfix release, previous version 15.03u13 suffering from a memory leak causing crashes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Globus GridFTP 11.8.4 - new build with 2 patches from DPM applied&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;dpm-dsi 1.9.13 - bug fix (dpm-gsiftp startup script seen to stop and then report daemon already running); use the new gridftp api to remove hack for gridftp redirection.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Davix 0.6.6 - bug fixes, see &lt;a href=&quot;http://dmc.web.cern.ch/release/davix-060&quot;&gt;release notes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;dmlite 0.8.6 - bug fix release bringing &lt;a href=&quot;http://lcgdm.web.cern.ch/dmlite-086-released-epel&quot;&gt;small changes&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;gfal2-utils 1.5.0 - &lt;a href=&quot;http://dmc.web.cern.ch/release/gfal2-util-1.5.0&quot;&gt;bug fixes/improvements&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;CERN Frontier squid 3.5.24-3.1 - see &lt;a href=&quot;http://frontier.cern.ch/dist/rpms-debug/frontier-squidRELEASE_NOTES&quot;&gt;release notes&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;ARC nagios-probes 1.9.1 - bug fixes, see &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nordugrid.org/arc/releases/15.03u14/release_notes_15.03u14.html&quot;&gt;release notes&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;QCG Broker 4.2.0 - added support for Array Jobs; instant information about resources for the new qcg-resources command; bug fixes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;gfal2-python 1.9.2 - see &lt;a href=&quot;http://dmc.web.cern.ch/release/gfal2-python-1.9.2&quot;&gt;release notes&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;XROOTD 4.6.1 - &lt;a href=&quot;http://xrootd.org/download/ReleaseNotes.html&quot;&gt;several new features and bug fixes&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;dCache 3.0.25 - see &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.dcache.org/downloads/1.9/release-notes-3.0.shtml#25&quot;&gt;release notes&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;FTS 3.6.8 - &lt;a href=&quot;http://fts3-service.web.cern.ch/documentation/releases#qt-release-ui-tabs3&quot;&gt;several new features and bug fixes&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;lcgdm 0.18.2 - bug fixes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;gfal2 2.13.4 - Default checksum for local copy was removed&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;br&gt;* CentOS7&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;APEL 1.5.1 - first release in UMD4/C7. Add support for Torque 5.1.2 time duration format; change dirq call to use absolute path to support versions of dirq &amp;gt;= 1.7; fix crash when StAR loader encouters a valid XML file with no records in it.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;APEL-SSM 2.1.7 - first release in UMD4/C7. Added a delay when receiver is reconnecting to improve reliability. Improved the log output for SSM receivers so that there are fewer trivial entries and so it's more useful in tracking messages on the filesystem. &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;CVMFS 2.3.5 - first release in UMD4/C7. Various bug fixes (see &lt;a href=&quot;http://cvmfs.readthedocs.io/en/2.3/cpt-releasenotes.html&quot;&gt;release notes&lt;/a&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;WN 4.0.5 - first release in UMD4/C7&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;DynaFed 1.3.1 - first release in UMD4/C7&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;ARC 15.03.14 - bugfix release, previous version 15.03u13 suffering from a memory leak causing crashes&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Globus GridFTP 11.8.4 - new build with 2 patches from DPM applied&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;dpm-dsi 1.9.13 - bug fix (dpm-gsiftp startup script seen to stop and then report daemon already running); use the new gridftp api to remove hack for gridftp redirection.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Davix 0.6.6 - bug fixes, see &lt;a href=&quot;http://dmc.web.cern.ch/release/davix-060&quot;&gt;release notes&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;dmlite 0.8.6 - bug fix release bringing &lt;a href=&quot;http://lcgdm.web.cern.ch/dmlite-086-released-epel&quot;&gt;small changes&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;gfal2-utils 1.5.0 - &lt;a href=&quot;http://dmc.web.cern.ch/release/gfal2-util-1.5.0&quot;&gt;bug fixes/improvements&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;CERN Frontier squid 3.5.24-3.1 - see &lt;a href=&quot;http://frontier.cern.ch/dist/rpms-debug/frontier-squidRELEASE_NOTES&quot;&gt;release notes&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;ARC nagios-probes 1.9.1 - bug fixes, see &lt;a href=&quot;http://www.nordugrid.org/arc/releases/15.03u14/release_notes_15.03u14.html&quot;&gt;release notes&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;QCG
